relation: apni zindagi k har shaam teray naam kar doon
Teray firaaq kay lamhay shumaar kartay howay
sher meray sab ghazlain meri sab teray nazranay hain
Teray Galay Mein Jo Bahon Ko Daal Rakhtay Hein
